casebody.data:
Otis WILLIAMS and Floyd N. Williams, etc., et al. v. A. L. NELSON. No. 9457. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. April 22, 1940. O. R. Baum and Ben Peterson, both of Pocatello, Idaho, for appellants. Jones, Pomeroy & Jones, of Pocatello, Idaho, and Jas. L. Conley, of Portland, Or., for appellee.

Before GARRECHT, HANEY, and HEALY, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

On motion of appellants for dismissal of appeal herein, and good cause therefor appearing, ordered appeal dismissed, that a decree of dismissal be filed and entered accordingly, and that mandate of this court issue forthwith.
